  "description": "<p>Features:<br/><br/>Chic, compact design, very beautiful.<br/>Specializing in the production of water rich in hydrogen.<br/>Made of high borosilicate glass and 304 stainless steel, it is of high quality and safe to use.<br/>It takes only 3 minutes to produce a cup of hydrogen-rich water that can be consumed directly.<br/>This is convenient at home or you need to take it with you.<br/>Romatic light glitters during the electrolysis process.<br/>Portable hydrogen-rich water electrolyzers provide you with healthier water.<br/>Hydrogen-rich water is easily absorbed, helps promote metabolism, and reduces constipation to some extent.<br/>Benefits of drinking water containing hydrogen:<br/><br/>1. Improve cell health and improve nutrient absorption<br/>2. Improve blood sugar and hba1c levels in diabetic patients<br/>3. Provide better moisturization to the body - increase blood circulation<br/>4. Helps reduce saturated fat content<br/>5. Reduce aging and make skin healthy<br/>6. Improve the memory of the elderly - reduce constipation problems<br/>7. Helps lower cholesterol levels.</p><h2>Black is out of stock and has an uncertain timeline. It is expected to be shipped in a few years<b id=\"dgtud\"></b></h2><p><br/></p><p>During the three-minute micro-electrolysis process of hydrogen production, it can be seen that water molecules will produce continuously rising bubbles after being broken down. The higher the mineral content in the water is, the stronger the electrolysis effect will be, and the higher the hydrogen content will be, thus rapidly changing the water quality in three minutes.&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p>Upgraded version: With a hydrogen content of up to 1600, it can be connected to mineral water bottles</p><p>Regular model: hydrogen content can reach 700-800,</p><p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17179776/2406100627290320600.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17179776/2406100627290321400.